{"type": "article", "id": 6331, "title": "Bollard 灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-16T07:40:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052343419HIb7vk1KnDl8TLS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦品牌 Menu 邀请美国设计师 Shane Schneck 在今年的哥本哈根 Northmodern 设计展上带来一款灯饰新作，由硅树脂材质制成，圆锥形的轮廓决定了其可以用来聚拢光源，定向照明，可以适用于 4 个位置的照射方式，垂直悬挂或者侧悬在天花板上皆可，竖放与横放于桌面作为小型台灯也可以。提供淡绿色、裸色、灰色以及黑色等选择。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234339GjuZFBwNOiX3YD0M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052343391mFyGOcMxAnkeVDP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.303125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234340HD9B32shb5FUx7lZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234340gyAeHhnWavOQU91p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}